caption.title: GO annotations related to genes suppressed by shutoff-active NS1.
caption.p: Enrichment analysis using GO Biological Process 2017b database of the 493 DEGs obtained from Fig 3A shows the pathways in which DEGs were suppressed by shutoff-active NS1 following virus infection. The ranking was based on the combined score, which was calculated from ln(P-value) Ã— Z-score (Enrichr).
